    <abstract id="aspace_052c1d6eeac02c8ad0ecb3b31cb46c79">The Brooklyn Fire Department publications includes the constitution and bylaws of the Village of Brooklyn Fire Department and reports, acts, prospectuses, and codes related to the Brooklyn Fire Department and its various iterations in the late 19th century.</abstract>
