  <acqinfo id="aspace_fbc09db76948bbd40676dac8d2848a5d">
    <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
<p>Source and date of acquisition unknown. The collection was formally accessioned in 1985.</p>  </acqinfo>
  <arrangement id="aspace_58cf5348c1010745af39d23dd8b7ece5">
    <head>Arrangement</head>
<p>The collection is arranged into three series by type. Within each series, materials are arranged chronologically.</p>  </arrangement>
  <prefercite id="aspace_49f586b3a7f9974ce9f433c61f71fc28">
